Former New England Patriots star Aaron Hernandez was found guilty on Wednesday of first-degree murder in a deadly late-night shooting , sealing the downfall of an athlete who once had a $ 40million contract and a standout career .
The first conviction conviction carries a mandatory sentence of life in prison without parole in the slaying of Odin Lloyd , a 27-year-old landscaper .
Lloyd was shot six times in the night on June 17 , 2013 in Hernandez 's home .